{bold}5. Features{nobold}{p}
-----------
{p} {p}
    - Cursor to edit text as a DTP editor{p}
    - New Imagemap Editor{p}
            now it's an external program linked by arexx commands{p}
    - Speedbar.mcc{p}
    - TearOff.mcc{p}
    - TextInput.mcc{p}
    - Nlist.mcc{p}
    - New Source Editor.{p}
            With coloured html tags.{p}
    - Cut, Copy, Paste to clipboard.{p}
    - New WYSIWYG <-> Source{p}
    - Single edit window{p}
    - Visual image sizing{p}
    - Visual Size table edition{p}
    - Wordwrap{p}
    - Support most important HTML tags{p}
    - WYSIWYG (What You See Is What You Get){p}
    - Easy Graphic Interface{p}
    - FRAMES support{p}
    - Metatools editor{p}
    - Embed object soported{p}
    - Source edition{p}
    - Easy WYSIWYG Imagemap edition!{p}
    - Arexx Commands{p}
    - Basic TABLE Support{p}
    - MetalWEB could be linked with Amiga best browsers using Arexx{p}
