{bold}System Requirements{nobold}{p}
-------------------{p}
{p} {p}
    Minimum:{p}
        - 2MB of free memory{p}
        - 68000 processor{p}
        - ECS{p}
        - MUI 3.8{p}
{p} {p}
    Recommended:{p}
        - 4MB of free memory{p}
        - Hard drive{p}
        - 68060 processor{p}
        - Workbench 3.0{p}
        - Gfx card{p}
        - MUI 3.8{p}
        - PPC Card with PPC datatypes{p}
